MULE_REPLY_TO_STOP_PROPERTY

public static final String MULE_REPLY_TO_STOP_PROPERTY
Prevents processing of the ReplyTo property by the Service. This is useful if you're component routed the message somewhere else which processed the ReplyTo.

SYNCHRONOUS_PROPERTY

public static final String SYNCHRONOUS_PROPERTY
Specifies whether mule should process messages sysnchonously, i.e. that a mule-model can only process one message at a time, or asynchronously. The default value is 'false'.
